{"tid":2077624,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網上流傳H＆M限制員工社交媒體言論   網民發起罷買","createTime":"2020-06-24T12:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T14:55:20.000Z","uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"82c44298091210fecfe8484cc11c7ac6beb519a1","tid":2077624,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:04:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/網上流傳h-m限制員工社交媒體言論-網民發起罷買-101925580.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%81%E5%82%B3h-m%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E7%BD%B7%E8%B2%B7-101925580.html&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=ce316e6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/網上流傳h-m限制員工社交媒體言論-網民發起罷買-101925580.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HwwmzW2YzyrYcN7QKDmEaQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/031c557d0bce29b34c685afa240f75e3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FHwwmzW2YzyrYcN7QKDmEaQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F031c557d0bce29b34c685afa240f75e3&h=2045dfe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上流傳指，H&amp;M近期修改員工守則，涉規管員工與工作時間外的言論自由，並對警告信條文進行修訂，並在未經商討情況下，要求員工簽署相關確認書，有網民呼籲市民共同支持員工，罷買該公司產品以作抵制，東網記者正就事件向該公司查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據指，新修訂的員工守則內容包含員工於私人時間在社交媒體發表之言論，員工或有可能因政治言論被解僱，有網民呼籲市民支持員工，罷買以作抵制該公司限制言論自由之行為。"},{"pid":"6e9df40682b596198a98d1c23b3cbf37133354bc","tid":2077624,"uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:06:13.000Z","msg":"邊個買h m就係鬼"},{"pid":"8267e09966d94b52a60692e8ed89a8c37c7347e3","tid":2077624,"uid":81562,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:08:40.000Z","msg":"啲衫洗兩次就鬆撚晒 你買埋我嗰份<img src=\"/assets/face